&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Successful candidates will be invited to an Assessment Day on Friday 18th Dec 2020 held at Bodmin. Please note this will be either a morning or afternoon session to be confirmed.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic compassionate registered nurses to join our team. The hospital has two wards one 19 bedded and one 25. Both wards specialise in rehabilitation but also take patients requiring palliative care. You will be part of a multi disciplinary team working together to achieve the best outcomes for patients. It is a nurse led unit which will offer you the opportunity to enhance your clinical skills, discharge planning and decision making. You will be supported in your professional development. CFT offer various opportunities for career progression.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post is permanent and involves internal rotation&lt;/p&gt;
